{"tid":1223783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不屑舞台界人拉票撐修例 甄詠蓓:藝術家不是為惡服務 屠夫說成慈母","createTime":"2019-06-14T19:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:23:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e73c1dfcab541cb5f5f92fe0c3e8edfb2a33534b","tid":1223783,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:34:59.000Z","msg":"在舞台劇界有份量，詹瑞文前妻甄詠蓓，昨晚在fb留言，稱在一個群組裡，見到一位她十分尊敬的人，為撐修例去拉票，令她相當難過。「每個人都有自由去做自己認為正確的事，或許有很多錯綜複雜背後原因，但我只想問一句，難道真的聽不到一百萬人遊行的聲音嗎？真的看不到警察過份使用武力嗎？看不到他們用橡膠子彈、催淚彈去射傷市民嗎？良知在那裡？」<br />\n<br />\n很多藝人因怕被內地打壓，影響生計的威脅，對撐港人反送中被迫選擇沉默，甄詠蓓就寧願他們沉默，都不要偽善。<br />\n<br />\n「最難過的是，藝術家應有的良知不能失去，藝術追求的是真善美，要撕開黑暗或醜惡的假面具&hellip;&hellip;而不是為惡而服務，甚至黑白不分，或是非顛倒，你可以沉默，但不能偽善。這就是這些年來，在戲劇藝術界教給我的，也是我們最基本的品格，也是作為藝人術能為此而驕傲的事情。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們不能善惡不分，魔得說成天使，屠夫說成是慈母。」<br />\n<br />\n甄詠蓓既是舞台劇演員，亦是導演、編作及導師，是香港少數女性戲劇創作人之一，在舞台界受人尊敬，不少藝人拜她為師學戲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190614/large/1560516670_b4bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190614%2Flarge%2F1560516670_b4bf.jpg&h=467e4389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190614/2_675984_0/-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%91%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E7%95%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8%E6%92%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%94%84%E8%A9%A0%E8%93%93-%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%83%A1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E5%B1%A0%E5%A4%AB%E8%AA%AA%E6%88%90%E6%85%88%E6%AF%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F2_675984_0%2F-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B1%2591%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2594%2584%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E8%2593%2593-%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2585%2588%25E6%25AF%258D&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8AomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=705cb2bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F2_675984_0%2F-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B1%2591%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2594%2584%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E8%2593%2593-%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2585%2588%25E6%25AF%258D&h=43cfd32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190614/2_675984_0/-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%91%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E7%95%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8%E6%92%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%94%84%E8%A9%A0%E8%93%93-%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%83%A1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E5%B1%A0%E5%A4%AB%E8%AA%AA%E6%88%90%E6%85%88%E6%AF%8D</a>"},{"pid":"a917308cdec5ddcc4a40bef286b6ad0d2950eb83","tid":1223783,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b3fc94f20725f43c37be1171d59409688f77cb0a","tid":1223783,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f90300220fb2dafe42054388251cd101d279fcca","tid":1223783,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"592e044874037f1bfaebea1a14489bae7ba11215","tid":1223783,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"難怪同條詹端文離婚啦<img src=\"/ass